<D>__{show me what it's like to be you. that's my last wish. grant it, lestat.}
<A>__{he stares at her, feeling some connection with this strange mortal girl. she stares at him with penetrating eyes. he again finds himself drawn to her. tries to fight it.}
<C>__{lestat}
<P>__{(turning away)}
<D>__{i don't have time for this.}
