<P>__{(softly)}
<D>__{right. the covens are coming for you.}
<P>__{(softly)}
<D>__{i understand why you're doing it. you have to be who you are, no matter what happens.}
<A>__{he turns, gazes at her. she steps forward.}
<C>__{jesse}
<D>__{but how are you spending what may be your last night on earth, lestat? as you always have... alone.}
